"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"给大家分享一个避雷的办法：多加一些维权群。一个项目如果跑路，就会有维权群，刚刚开始维权群会要各种负能量.骂人的.报警的等什么都有，然后维权群会静下来，过几天群就会有各种各样的土狗来推荐。重点来了！维权群推荐的币全都不要买！这么简单的措施能避很多雷。 \\n 不要问我为什么有那么多维权群\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/ux5QdDwjVryvOakYgOpX3.png?height=1016&width=723)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640747081,\"title\":\"给大家分享一个避雷的办法\"},\"digest\":\"UIEbEgi4boEIZM3xAMOS14g49MaVEejC_gyECGDX_uM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9c8cB6406C3943C4f29998eE24E1E0da9c1cf32E\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"M-lTyYSzAsxlV4wbxPMnM6yQI1PiGFBxZBZpPwbb7fc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XPqOnfPBDPbQyyVGDq3CB9hZOpx7Hmz9Jla4GTf-dl8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6bm47V7-QS9QyiqXYZNIJH0YXf_rkRURA7OKWn80pUoIPgHq8qiJi-eFObkCX_pBXpqVl3bXyTKK5NURoQJ4nA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x0cfd6d6dbded88d6386c39c5b121f061bd33576a9dab401c02a45364e8a0c2fd081aca69217a01c306d2bc4b64e833da22e048eb73111863f921190a3486e8c61c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"M-lTyYSzAsxlV4wbxPMnM6yQI1PiGFBxZBZpPwbb7fc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"XPqOnfPBDPbQyyVGDq3CB9hZOpx7Hmz9Jla4GTf-dl8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"UIEbEgi4boEIZM3xAMOS14g49MaVEejC_gyECGDX_uM\"}"